dBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T13:52:14.000Z","msg":"我好容易發清醒夢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我記得發個一個夢係類似我俾人捉咗<br />\n但係我已經知道自己發緊夢<br />\n之後醒咗 做返日常正常會做嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n突然之間鬧鐘響咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來係夢中夢 以為自己好勁識破咗個夢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最尾都係俾個夢呃咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b6f9f6d261331eb22463ded640c39528fcd2bf3","tid":108761,"uid":33770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T13:54:12.000Z","msg":"成曰夢見同一個女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a0d63ffe296cca4164eed3dec251eb8885e36d","tid":108761,"uid":59654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T13:55:57.000Z","msg":"發夢殺人<br />\n用條繩勒死人"},{"pid":"a9893235f684f701970ac96559cd8e6da5f9cf42","tid":108761,"uid":13454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T13:56:19.000Z","msg":"係夢入面落大雨 你係涼亭同我講你中意我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c829b45df47331eb372c3f1e8c6d3d848a9f1286","tid":108761,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:42:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係夢入面落大雨 你係涼亭同我講你中意我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a710664dc642b540ac3616fedc563bb182fc57b7","tid":108761,"uid":27425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T18:39:02.000Z","msg":"發夢我全家比人追殺<br />\n之後我就殺死哂想殺我地嘅殺手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d209f66b5c9c07d1907f816fc97d50782cd51dd","tid":108761,"uid":22384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T18:41:10.000Z","msg":"前晚夢到自己中左六合彩二獎<br />\n但淨係記得其中三個字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cac1e699242faaecba640f3396ce66a13889a34","tid":108761,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T18:42:26.000Z","msg":"睇得多喪屍片<br />\n細個成日夢見點係屋企生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4082e09b85fd5f53579976e707613a9e9a5e9412","tid":108761,"uid":58246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T18:49:12.000Z","msg":"成個畫面都係玻璃紙隻紅色咁<br />\n夢到有日朝早親戚忽然黎哂我屋企 有個人掘我天花板<br />\n然後掘到個神主牌 係我表哥<br />\n我表哥當時係到 嗰個人同我表哥講左啲嘢 我聽唔到 但我表哥呆哂<br />\n最怪係我嗰陣一瞇埋眼就繼續個夢 一開眼就停 不停咁loop 個人半訓之間又醒唔到"},{"pid":"e2bce22047f9cd94400e561482aeac2856d83b2b","tid":108761,"uid":54176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T19:32:56.000Z","msg":"就黎入到個閪 黎耀祥跳出黎捉住我碌鳩 嚇醒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1decd4af18e83fd4e56b620d616a67d6e4168f9","tid":108761,"uid":28223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T19:39:51.000Z","msg":"夢見自己返返去中學上緊堂既情景  完全唔想醒返想繼續發落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d420898d4d996a1ebc6f2cc431f97b3dd344c13","tid":108761,"uid":25689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T19:51:32.000Z","msg":"夢見同中意左10年既女仔一齊行街 拖手<br />\n結合係點 已經唔記得 <br />\n始終都係夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"512e75edf3ee0dc567f58f19df06b56c42e31987","tid":108761,"uid":1274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T20:18:05.000Z","msg":"會成日夢到以前中學一個老師，<br />\n但明明現實根本同佢唔熟，甚至零交流。<br />\n<br />\n夢過落暴雨，狂閃電，勁響嘅雷聲，耳仔就嚟震聾，大雨到啲水衝入屋咁制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n嚇醒之後間房好靜，凌晨五點幾，攤喺張床望住天花板，有啲呆&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"1b168cb364f101deca9c257ff9f04a89f7d79b3d","tid":108761,"uid":1274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T20:23:38.000Z","msg":"因為晚晚發夢，所以有記錄夢嘅習慣，放本簿喺枕頭隔離，或者寫喺手機（但手機啲光容易導致完全清醒）<br />\n有時唔俾自己完全清醒，一邊發夢一邊用筆記低，<br />\n記完一部分，跟住再發埋剩餘果啲情節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無人明我講咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5281ee04572e1ef73d08370add12eacf98fa72","tid":108761,"uid":74484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T21:33:12.000Z","msg":"比人追殺緊，戈時我老撚咁向前跑，跑跑下比人用長矛由後腦向前插，戈個感覺好真實"},{"pid":"b09f9b52512af262e9a1e69e0effa046fae4a29e","tid":108761,"uid":60936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T21:52:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為晚晚發夢，所以有記錄夢嘅習慣，放本簿喺枕頭隔離，或者寫喺手機（但手機啲光容易導致完全清醒）<br />\n有時唔俾自己完全清醒，一邊發夢一邊用筆記低，<br />\n記完一部分，跟住再發埋剩餘果啲情節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無人明我講咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我訓醒後仲記得情節會寫落手機備忘錄度"},{"pid":"88402ec9b829c89e8465cc41ee422c8b5166ec43","tid":108761,"uid":57271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T21:55:01.000Z","msg":"俾一堆mk仔圍<br />\n然後俾人扔落街，不過着地之後竟然仲行動得走得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82b4b54590f64387b2157b71bcecb550e762f576","tid":108761,"uid":10545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T17:30:45.000Z","msg":"發夢樓主俾隻曱甴壁咚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ff609c19c6df2ae9a862adc020b442722bab537","tid":108761,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply